menu "AS120 Configuration"
    config SIMULATE_I2C
        bool "Simulate I2C devices (no PCB required)"
        default n
        help
            When enabled, all I2C communication is simulated.
            The TCA9535 GPIO expanders and DAC7574 DACs will not
            be accessed on the I2C bus, and home switch inputs
            will be simulated. This allows running the firmware
            on a bare ESP32-S3 devkit without the PCB attached.
endmenu
